---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="Start Here | Eco Living Journey" description="Your beginner roadmap for eco-friendly living in apartments." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />

    <main class="container">
      <h1>Start Here: The Beginner Roadmap</h1>
      <p>Start small. Save money. Avoid overwhelm. This is the fastest way to build habits that last.</p>

      <h2>Step 1 — Pick one room</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/kitchen/">Kitchen (easiest wins)</a></li>
        <li><a href="/cleaning/">Cleaning (health + budget)</a></li>
        <li><a href="/bathroom/">Bathroom (low-waste basics)</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Step 2 — Use the “3-rule”</h2>
      <p>Only buy a swap if it’s: (1) practical, (2) affordable, and (3) you’ll actually use it.</p>

      <h2>Step 3 — Build your starter kit</h2>
      <p>Once you’ve done 3–5 swaps, you’ll know your style and can upgrade smarter.</p>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; }
  h2 { margin-top: 2rem; }
</style>